      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        About <br /> Pelagornis</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
